# Project 3: Math Operators (JavaScript)

This project demonstrates basic JavaScript math operators and how to display results on a webpage using HTML event handlers and DOM manipulation.

## Features / Requirements Covered
- Functions using the following operators:
  - Addition `+`
  - Subtraction `-`
  - Multiplication `*`
  - Division `/`
  - Modulus `%`
  - Increment `++`
  - Decrement `--`
- A function using `Math.random()`
- HTML elements + event handlers (buttons) for each function
- Comments throughout the JavaScript code explaining what each function does

